data.description:
Home remodeled, up graded with addition added. 
  Huge master bedroom with his and hers organized closets and electric fire place with in wall wires for wall mounted tv.  Master bathroom has his and hers sink, double enclosed jacuzzi steam shower with all the bells and whistles.  Master bedroom also has a small sitting area as well as stairs to stand up attic that can be finished and stairs to two car attached garage and possible weight room. 
    House has a lot of new, up graded remodeled rooms master bedroom just being one of them.  Contact for more information.
data.whatILove: Private secluded setting just minutes from everything.
